		<label>Make mild steel x35</label>
		<description>TIER 3 - Industrial	
>>> Optimal 	Economy
>> Suitable 	Construction
X Inadvisable 	Armor, Blades
			
Tools Recommended: None/Any (below average, economical)
			
An economical metal, mild steel would be the modern equivalent to wrought iron. It's also called a low-carbon steel. Soft and ductile, it's easily formed and welded. It's galvanized with a zinc coating to prevent corrosion, and as bonus, gives it antimicrobial properties.</description>
